{"tid":664441,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［懷舊台］一人一個自己最好睇嘅post","createTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T08:13:02.000Z","uid":2023,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e30408fad378535b59d4beee75dd68fa4e69f823","tid":664441,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"放假悶得濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故、起底、批鬥、撚狗公、膠、自爆、遊記...咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比啲好睇嘅post黎打發下時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便宣傳下自己個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［偷圖者死全家］福島玩命之旅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611900/page/6?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611900/page/6?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"b0983400c28a9857112f7603fd1786e4f793b83c","tid":664441,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"Me=all"},{"pid":"38cf6bfed88740d6f7fd4d67290a6f42c04e1fef","tid":664441,"uid":2023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0983400c28a9857112f7603fd1786e4f793b83c","tid":664441,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"Me=all"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"All唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128c392989464d38189393948697d9c3ae398035","tid":664441,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"上年個神秘電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7a28ddd9456226e39d37397a80987529e6fff6","tid":664441,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"呢個post本來諗住假膠下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為無咩人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開完個post就去左返工<br />\n點知放lunch個陣見到咁多正皮上埋熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗咁都有得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後變埋鬧戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢隻是咪白紋e蚊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/242358/page/18?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/242358/page/18?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1e7dad51b8534147dd2d88dbf90bcdc3cd6780a","tid":664441,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"128c392989464d38189393948697d9c3ae398035","tid":664441,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"上年個神秘電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"Post出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咁多post"},{"pid":"9e134ef46e72a1251a269e19a94a2cf50c0e2571","tid":664441,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"冇個好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7fa9f652048a1a1958b994f93df0cb4b132b0f","tid":664441,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e134ef46e72a1251a269e19a94a2cf50c0e2571","tid":664441,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"冇個好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"幽靈感同創意呢啲野天生嘅<i